Priority:
    * Attempt to auto-reconnect when a connection is lost

Ideas:
    * Allow recording the song that is being played
        * Have a menu item with a "recording" icon that when pressed will start saving the song
          then when pressed again it will stop recording and save the song
    * Allow recording / uploading new instruments
        * Allow editing these instruments - but not allowed to edit pre-installed instruments
        * When selecting an instrument, have 2 columns to show user defined instruments and default instruments